text: Hamdiah Damanhuri is an Indonesian archer. She was born on 16 November 1973. Damanhuri competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Hamdiah DamanhuriHamdiah DAMANHURI == References == Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian archers Category:Olympians for Indonesia
